Megatron chuckeld to himself and took control, sending their ship 
blasting downwards, narowly missing a mine in the process. "I am 
picking up your Stunticons at a position outside of base Motormaster, 
with another robot". Motormaster stood up, and clenched his huge fist, 
"There had better not be treachery afoot, death to all traitors," 
Motormaster said in his booming emosionless voice, as he turned his 
angry snarl towards Switchblade. "Now come Switchblade, do not be like 
that" replied Megatron. "You are being part of history. We set down 
and begin another push, on the Cybertronion Fire" he comanded, as they 
began to reenter from outerspace.
